      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of August 20 headline about Chloe Sevigny, not Segivny, actress whose clothing style is admired (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A headline last Sunday about an actress who is admired in the world of fashion despite appearing to treat it with indifference misspelled her surname. As the article noted, she is Chloe Sevigny, not Segivny.</p>
      </block>
